Recommended Architecture
Component 	Recommended Setup	Why?

Long Term Memory (LTM)	Dedicated Server	Memory requir	des specialized vector storage and semantic indexing. Keeping it separate allows you to optimize retrieval without slowing down other tools.

Resource Bank			Dedicated Server	Resources are data-heavy. A separate server prevents high-traffic data fetching from blocking real-time conversational responses or tool execution.

Agent Tools				Grouped by Domain	Group tools by functionality (e.g., a "Productivity Server" for your agents). This prevents "token bloat" where the AI is overwhelmed by too many tool descriptions at once.

0TTS Models				Async / Standalone	TTS involves heavy media processing. It is best handled by an async server that can manage audio streams without timing out the main context protocol.